OL,4,CJust 20 firms behind more than half of
OL,5,Csingle-use plastic waste - study
OL,6, Just 20 companies are the source of
OL,7, more than half of all the single-use
OL,8, plastic items thrown away globally.
OL,10,FThat's the conclusion of analysis of
OL,11,Fthe corporate network behind plastic
OL,12,Fproduction.
OL,14,FThe study looked at approximately 1,000
OL,15,Ffactories that make the raw materials
OL,16,Fneeded for single-use products.
OL,18,FPlastic bottles, food packages and bags
OL,19,Fare among billions of items that are
OL,20,Fused once and then thrown away, often
OL,21,Fending up in the oceans.
